room_title: Escape room "The Office of the Double Agent 33" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
room_address: 1425 Wisconsin Dells Parkway Suite 3 Wisconsin Dells, WI 53965
room_description:
It’s the height of the 1940’s. You have strong intel suggesting that your top agent, Agent 33, is suspected of being a double agent and laundering money from US Government Agencies directly to the oil companies in the middle east. Analysts have decoded encrypted messages showing Agent 33 has ties to an unknown individual, The Boss.
Your mission is to track the whereabouts of Agent 33 and find out the identity of The Boss. Failure will result in Agent 33’s escape and The Boss’s identity remaining a mystery. Will you get the information and escape in time?
